{"tid":1535310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無左民間記者會？","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:12:56.000Z","uid":263079,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"954561510c830dbe17d03b5213c869f8c0ac46fb","tid":1535310,"uid":263079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:09:33.000Z","msg":"其實之前搞民間記者會一路反應都幾好<br />\n又可以做到最好既文宣效果<br />\n點解宜家冇左既？"},{"pid":"8d442963a521079e21976fc1dd0adb383287a431","tid":1535310,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"863bacb231b8b38af6f031d35cb858ec90c60cb1","tid":1535310,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5fd57a301e550c32ef05c22dda68bf79760ced6","tid":1535310,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4baed552e2e349504d090d10577d32c766d9954","tid":1535310,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XGsKsXy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXGsKsXy.gif&h=2996ed29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gTp1AJS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgTp1AJS.png&h=24c3c0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnxyoC2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnxyoC2.gif&h=9a775d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9月8日撐法案萬人祈禱集會</span></span><br />\n地點：遮打花園 美國駐港澳總領事館<br />\n時間：9月8日 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">12:30</span></strong> (遮打)  <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">14:00</span></strong> (美領)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">宗教集會，不需申請不反對通知書，自行評估風險<br />\n(因鄰近禮賓府，很大機會不獲批，反而不合法)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">行動：</span><br />\n由教徒帶領為香港人權及民主祈禱<br />\n提交巨式請願信，並供在場人士簽署<br />\n喊叫英文號，包括撐法案訴求<br />\n&quot;Free Hong Kong, Pass the act.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">活動為和理非，不容許有任何衝擊行為</span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">時間表：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Skc24zk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkc24zk.png&h=3cadacbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2xyrND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2xyrND.png&h=1b101412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12：30 遮打花園祈禱集會，評估人數<br />\n13：30 不經禮賓府，沿金鍾道紅棉路方向前往美領<br />\n13：50 經過花園道聖若瑟堂，唱聖歌及祈禱<br />\n14：00 美國領事館祈禱集會 <br />\n(如人數太多，以流水式在美領對出繞圈集會)<br />\n15：30  提交巨式請願信 / 請願信<br />\n17：00  離開禮賓府及美領相關範圍 (<span style=\"color: red;\">和平散去</span>)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">目前要做：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n1. 一人一信向美領通知集會+表達訴求</span><br />\n<br />\n電話: (852) 2523-9011<br />\n電子郵件: information_resource_center_hk@yahoo.com<br />\n電子郵件: HKPressTeam@state.gov<br />\n<br />\n範本：<br />\nDear sir or madam,<br />\n<br />\nAccording to the information from the web and social platform, there will be a peaceful assembly outside your office (Consulate General of the US) at Hong Kong time 14:00 on 8th September,2016 (this Sunday) in which a petition for the urge of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act will be expressed and a letter is hoped to be passed to your officer.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, I am writing to hopefully notify you for the event and ask that if there will be special arrangement such as assigning a officer to receive the letter on that day? It would be appreciated.<br />\n<br />\nI am also a supporter of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act. And I hope the voice of the Hong Kong people can be delivered to the US and related department.Thank you.<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\n(你的名字)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>2. 需要有英文好巴寫請願信</strong></span><br />\n正常SIZE 及 巨型請願信各一封<br />\n巨型請願信內文較簡單，供集會人士簽署<br />\n如冇職員接信，正常SIZE星期一遞交<br />\n巨型請願信則放在美領門口，如圖<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezgfFmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezgfFmt.jpg&h=2f5218bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>3. 打印當日文宣及道具(如美國旗)</strong></span><br />\n建議一人一國旗，下面可打印：<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9UdrvE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9UdrvE.png&h=c7454fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7aj6wD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7aj6wD.png&h=b55903f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nrCiDc6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnrCiDc6.png&h=68b4225c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOLoPk2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOLoPk2.png&h=27b41922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>4. 入TG討論公海</strong></span><br />\n入TG討論詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=d3e414c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4f0714938fc4fe1bbed82cc7ed9cc1d976167328","tid":1535310,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"我諗好多都係外地巴絲，佢地D英文真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02324eec1d066470b0cc03c74781949aa49fb294","tid":1535310,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:11:45.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"8a3b7333d110daae455dfa947557f2add64a0697","tid":1535310,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16baeb9e8af23ec6946e288704f9f29bf5aecd78","tid":1535310,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699f8c955a87576e4fd40e323be0dd32f2014e22","tid":1535310,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"我都想知"},{"pid":"0fc3f5ce47eaad0ce620472b3a646ec864886607","tid":1535310,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fb7a71e1fac889fd05604d1bb8c40399d4df402","tid":1535310,"uid":45035,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"冇大家報名去講野 講完"},{"pid":"6615a0ad9d98f44c02307c07851a43c2f2268316","tid":1535310,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"可能係搵緊831資料?"},{"pid":"23a97269b2118040ad9f824c15a25c9bb7b65fbf","tid":1535310,"uid":53172,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:15:35.00